  <brief_title>Study to Investigate the Safety and Pharmacokinetics of SER120 Nasal Spray in Elderly Patients With Nocturia</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase III Randomized, Open-Label, Multicenter Study to Investigate the Safety and Pharmacokinetics of SER120 Nasal Spray Formulations in Elderly Patients (â‰¥ 75 Years Old) With Nocturia</official_title>
