  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine if SER120 nasal spray is well tolerated in 75 years
      or older nocturic patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Patients entering the study are randomized to either Level 1 SER120 nasal spray concentration
      or Level 2 SER120 nasal spray concentration
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
