  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Male &amp; female greater or equal to 75 years of age, history of nocturia

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  CHF, Diabetes, Diabetes Insipidus, Renal Insufficiency, Heptatic Insufficiency,
             Incontinence, Illness requiring steroid, current or past urologic maliganancy,
             nephrotic syndrome

          -  Unexplained pelvic masses

          -  Urinary bladder surgery or radiotherapy

          -  Sleep apnea
